'''''We Could Be Heroes''''' ni film ya siporo ya documentaire yo muri [[Maroke|Maroc yo muri]] 2018 iyobowe na Hind Bensari kandi yakozwe na Habib Attia na Vibeke Vogel kuri Bullitt Films<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/52327_1</ref><ref>https://maroc-diplomatique.net/a-oslo-we-could-be-heroes-distille-une-emotion-a-fleur-de-peau/</ref>.  Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Azeddine Nouiri, wabaye nyampinga w’imikino Paralympiqu<ref>https://femmesdumaroc.com/actualite/we-could-be-heroes-le-documentaire-emouvant-de-hind-bensari-46543</ref>e, watsinze imbogamizi z’umubiri zatoranijwe mu mikino Paralympike ya Rio 2016 hamwe n’inshuti ye Youssef akiri umwana<ref>http://www.docmonde.org/we-could-be-heroes/</ref>. 

Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere ku ya 2 Gicurasi 2018 muri Theatre ya Scotiabank <ref>https://fr.hespress.com/29668-casablanca-projection-en-avant-premiere-du-documentaire-we-could-be-heroes-de-hind-bensari.html</ref>.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.   Filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Jury mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Documentaire Hot Docs<ref>https://www.festivalmarrakech.info/film/we-could-be-heroes/</ref> . Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye "Igihembo cyiza cya International Documentary Award" mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto.  Filime yatsindiye Grand Prix mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Tangier<ref>https://fr.le360.ma/culture/festival-du-film-de-tanger-le-documentaire-we-could-be-heroes-de-bensari-remporte-le-grand-prix-de-185671</ref> <ref>http://www.africine.org/film/lancer-ce-poids-we-could-be-heroes-160615761590-1575160415711576159115751604/19928</ref>. 

